: "Love has ways of bringing things back to life. All you said was hi. And I remembered I loved you. Came back when it mattered. I saw you standing there in the light of the window wearing that same smile. Man, it's been a while. But I knew it, I knew you. I knew you.", "history": [{"date": "2026-07-18", "plays": 39618, "likes": 308, "comments": 13}, {"date": "2026-07-19", "plays": 136092, "likes": 1210, "comments": 46}], "still_climbing": true, "hook_type": "Personal Experience", "is_relevant": false}, {"shortCode": "Da4hbWOSryx", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/Da4hbWOSryx/", "caption": "You\u2019ll never lose your suitcase again with tip #6! \ud83c\udf0d\u2708\ufe0f Save this before your next trip! I\u2019ve used Samsonite suitcases for the last 10 years as I find they\u2019re the best quality and durability. Their new Paralux range is amazing as it comes with packing cubes that fit the suitcase perfectly, dual access opening (so you can access your stuff quickly without fully unpacking!) and even a built-in AirTag holder! Such a clever and practical design! Which tip did you not know? @samsonite_au @luxury.escapes \n\n#packinghacks #packwithme #traveltips #travelhacks", "timestamp": "2026-07-17T06:02:39.000Z", "videoDuration": 35.177, "videoPlayCount": 192854, "videoViewCount": null, "likesCount": 1584, "commentsCount": 54, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-sea5-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/749183990_18101012537190993_6042646970435402420_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-sea5-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=109&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGFiyvVz_gk3PWkGnFQYDC0IBxklcTo3NF_VFG5Zmse3x3h51k7GH_bZwRZiQRACF8&_nc_ohc=-OUCxYQsSpkQ7kNvwECGySq&_nc_gid=4Hm-OJMMWOdFTqBNMKtIRg&edm=ADp7STQBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQAwzjiy8de12TotxLUWl3tBZYkMjjd6I0Sf1i9jP6PlDw&oe=6A6225AF&_nc_sid=c6f216", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-lga3-2.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m86/AQP1kQ2i54tIqsr8HCUI8SJmzAbKQ9ZJRD927pxVrEAbNLLE6QsTKNSTcgGedp50w_QW-fXjhQOpFrIWgNmlE-4KxarmQWFKND3LxcU.mp4?_nc_c