 "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "27188639770758551"}, "ownerUsername": "mama_mila_au", "ownerFullName": "Chantel Mila", "transcript": "Have you ever wondered how luxury hotels get their towels looking so plush? Here's the trick. Fold one corner into a triangle, then fold it in half and flip the towel around. From the flat side, roll towards the pointed end, then tuck in that end. This fold is one of my favourites. It takes around 10 seconds to do and creates that little simple hotel moment at home.", "history": [{"date": "2026-07-18", "plays": 312114, "likes": 2564, "comments": 25}, {"date": "2026-07-19", "plays": 312824, "likes": 2582, "comments": 25}], "still_climbing": false, "hook_type": "Secret Reveal / Breakdown", "is_relevant": true}]}